videos.description: Cincinnati's Malik Clements sacks McKenzie Milton, who also fumbles in the end zone and Kimoni Fitz recovers for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Bearcats force sack fumble for TD

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton fakes the handoff and then rushes forward for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Milton keeps it himself for the TD

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton lobs a pass to Adrian Killins Jr. in the end zone, who makes the diving catch for the score.
videos.headline: Killins makes diving TD grab

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton drops a perfect pass to Tre Nixon, who waltzes into the end zone for the score.
videos.headline: Milton drops perfect TD pass to Nixon

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton shovels a pass forward to Adrian Killins Jr., who avoids tacklers and goes 42-yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Milton's quick shovel pass turns into TD

videos.description: UCF RB Greg McCrae takes the handoff and manuevers his way in for a 9-yard touchdown to extend the Golden Knights' lead.
videos.headline: McCrae finds his way in for the TD

videos.description: McKenzie Milton leads UCF with 268 yards passing, 3 TDs in the air and one on the ground as the Knights clinch the AAC East division.
